{"tid":1389260,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"想知皇馬對上一次嬴波係幾時？","createTime":"2019-07-31T00:53:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-31T06:31:22.000Z","uid":217108,"like":10,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"1daf046c09ec45e26eae1a107d67aedf9003fd44","tid":1389260,"uid":217108,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T00:53:10.000Z","msg":"唔計要互射十二碼黎決定果d<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5544cafdf10247cd02945cff9c75935571d330f","tid":1389260,"uid":5190,"like":6,"dislike":4,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T00:54:37.000Z","msg":"對得住前線！對得住義士！<br />\n一日政府無回應 一日都要繼續抗爭！<br />\n一個都不能少！<br />\n堅持五大訴求！！！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">一、徹底撤回修例<br />\n二、收回暴動定義<br />\n三、撤銷對今為所有反送中抗爭者控罪<br />\n四、徹底追究警隊濫權情況<br />\n五、以行政命令解散立法會，立即實行雙真普選<br />\n</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: teal;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">也試過太衝動 大件事沒計輕重<br />\n錯過悔過仍要衝 衝出困局<br />\n形象似義勇軍<span style=\"color: violet;\">(crusade)</span>般英勇<br />\n但結果有沒有停戰的溝通?<span style=\"color: violet;\">(訴求？)</span><br />\n如戴著面具<span style=\"color: violet;\">(mask)</span>去掩飾倦容<br />\n迎著炮火也依然表情輕鬆<span style=\"color: violet;\">(不屈？)</span><br />\n情緒不可激動 還若輕的舉重<br />\n來化解一切壓力似失蹤<br />\n如放下面具去也許面紅<span style=\"color: violet;\">(憤怒？)</span><br />\n乘著晚風去追尋逍遙星空<br />\n除去假的寬容 還真想不通<br />\n曾年少的青蔥 懷著理想那怕痛<span style=\"color: violet;\">(revolution)</span></span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TfDAuxC.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTfDAuxC.png&h=60385d7c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gnOwNja.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgnOwNja.png&h=f5b7bc3c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"c88d5c9a5492bc593c96ad563163192ed5fea9f0","tid":1389260,"uid":64710,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T04:05:46.000Z","msg":"果時我未出世<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />利申20歲"},{"pid":"ebffdd7fad5602e6767339c77ac6973dcbc1fbf0","tid":1389260,"uid":217108,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T04:44:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22ec4b89395e3d0a80d0e2a77a19168386b7756d","tid":1389260,"uid":54373,"like":3,"dislike":5,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"1daf046c09ec45e26eae1a107d67aedf9003fd44","tid":1389260,"uid":217108,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T00:53:10.000Z","msg":"唔計要互射十二碼黎決定果d<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T04:46:46.000Z","msg":"你唔好理，輸親波朗迷就會出來話係無咗佢個c朗"},{"pid":"ec5c44e4c9f9970dc1db368f2308e336ed69fe76","tid":1389260,"uid":217108,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"22ec4b89395e3d0a80d0e2a77a19168386b7756d","tid":1389260,"uid":54373,"like":3,"dislike":5,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"1daf046c09ec45e26eae1a107d67aedf9003fd44","tid":1389260,"uid":217108,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T00:53:10.000Z","msg":"唔計要互射十二碼黎決定果d<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T04:46:46.000Z","msg":"你唔好理，輸親波朗迷就會出來話係無咗佢個c朗"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T04:48:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />仲朗迷 唔係講緊祖記"},{"pid":"a3ea392f2ae26aac42d1e26c7e19d11168a1c973","tid":1389260,"uid":54373,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score